title: Ep 31 - Success Made Simple: The One Thing w/ Jay Papasan
itunes:title: Ep 31 - Success Made Simple: The One Thing w/ Jay Papasan
description:
In this episode Rob interviews Jay Papasan, author of the best selling book "The One Thing" Jay speaks in depth about the six lies we tell ourselves that keep us from being successful. He also tells us why the happiest people in the world are always the ones who know their "one thing" and follow it with all their hearts.
